ygData.subject: Re: EQ Patches Update
ygData.msgSnippet: Paladin and SK one are still under testing. IF it comes live, the paladin one will be in Rathe mountains at the paladin camp, and SK one at Mistmoore.
ygData.messageBody:
Paladin and SK one are still under testing. IF it comes live, the paladin one will be in Rathe
mountains at the paladin camp, and SK one at Mistmoore.
